Installation
============

*** Detailed and long version ***


Dot-Vim installation
--------------------

Clone dot-vim project:

    $ git clone https://github.com/hklausing/dotvim.git

Create symlinks:

    $ ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    $ cd ~/.vim
    $ git submodule init
    $ git submodule update


Plugin: Vundle
--------------

The defined vim plugins have to initialized via a function call 
within vim.

Launch vim:

    $ vim

and run following command:

    :PluginInstall



*** Quick installation ***

Script install.sh
-----------------

The script install.sh does all the steps defines above.
Start the script:

    $ cd ~/.vim
    $ ./install.sh


